content:
Here are some feelings that are not necessarily #depression:
-sadness
-fatigue 
-discouragement 
-dismay 
-overwhelmed 
-lethargy 
-sorrow
-loss(mourning) 

Not every “down” feeling is depression. 

#MentalHealthAwarenessMonth
